# Sounds Directory

This directory is for Halloween game sound effects and background music.

## Recommended Audio Files:
- `spooky-background.mp3` - Background music (optional)
- `success.mp3` - Success sound effect
- `click.mp3` - Button click sound
- `error.mp3` - Error feedback sound

## Audio Format Support:
- MP3 (recommended for compatibility)
- WAV (higher quality, larger files)
- OGG (good compression, modern browsers)

## Usage:
Audio files are optional. The game works perfectly without them, but they enhance the spooky atmosphere!